OL,3,CBristol Bears star subject of new
OL,4,Cdocumentary exploring sport and
OL,5,Cmotherhood
OL,7,FA rugby player who returned to the
OL,8,Fpitch just months after giving birth
OL,9,Fhas said she wanted to document her
OL,10,Fexperience "to help future
OL,11,Fgenerations".
OL,13,FAbbie Ward, who plays for Bristol
OL,14,FBears and England Rugby, is the
OL,15,Fsubject of a new film exploring the
OL,16,Fchallenges faced by professional
OL,17,Ffemale athletes and working mothers.
