OL,3,CBristol Bears star subject of new
OL,4,Cdocumentary exploring sport and
OL,5,Cmotherhood
OL,7,FThe hour-long ITVX film, 'A Bump in
OL,8,Fthe Road,' follows Ms Ward's journey
OL,9,Fto get back to playing rugby, just 17
OL,10,Fweeks after the birth of her first
OL,11,Fchild in July 2023.
OL,13,FMs Ward said she decided to take part
OL,14,Fin the documentary "so people could
OL,15,Fsee what it is like" returning to
OL,16,Fprofessional sport as a mother.
OL,18,FThe Bristol Bears and England Rugby
OL,19,Fstar said she had "no idea" what it
OL,20,Fwould mean for her as a player when
OL,21,Fshe announced her pregnancy.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
