OL,7,F"The coaches didn't have any idea
OL,8,Feither, nor did the physios or the
OL,9,Fnutritionists," she said.
OL,11,F"It was all a steep learning curve.
OL,13,F"I wanted to make sure that we could
OL,14,Fget as much learning from everything I
OL,15,Fwent through, to help the next players
OL,16,Falong, and the next generation," she
OL,17,Fadded.
