OL,7,FShe said her plan was always to get
OL,8,Fback on the pitch "as soon as
OL,9,Fpossible" after giving birth, but that
OL,10,Fit's hard to explain to people "the
OL,11,Fpressures and the guilt that you feel".
OL,13,FAbbie said: "I think, as a Mum,
OL,14,Fsometimes you just can't win.
OL,16,F"There's so many pressures, there's so
OL,17,Fmany people saying you should do it
OL,18,Fthis way, you should do it that way.
