OL,7,F"It's really hard, it's hard to
OL,8,Fexplain that to other people, the
OL,9,Fpressures and the guilt that you feel.
OL,11,F"So I wanted to go out there and show
OL,12,Fmy plan was ambitious, I was lucky to
OL,13,Fbe able to do that.
OL,15,F"There are so many people saying you
OL,16,Fshould do it this way, or you should
OL,17,Fdo it that way.
OL,19,F"It's been a whirlwind hasn't it? But
OL,20,Fwe're loving every minute, it's great.
OL,21,FIt's going amazingly."
